commits.commitMessage:
GMSK Tx burst console commands for PHY SDK

New variable PHY_SDK_CONSOLE_COMMANDS added in high level Makefile to enable to distinguish "pure PHY SDK build" (i.e. for RF unit tests - Smart CLI console commands) from classical build (2G modem PHY code).
PHY_SDK_CONSOLE_COMMANDS = true means ue_lte.fw image will be compatible with Smart CLI tool and PHY_SDK_CONSOLE_COMMANDS = false means phy.elf image can be used and combined with a 2G MAC image.

Integration of new console commands enabling to use GSM hardcoded Tx burst and to set the timing of 2G FEM Rx/Tx switch.
Include two pythons script to be used with Altair Smart CLI console commands:
Automation\RF test scripts\rf_script_rx.py
Automation\RF test scripts\rf_script_tx.py

Resolves: ALT1250-955
Change-Id: I4ab3f05d22715c6d553de67cbf3ef58d8ba90984
